    "body" : "<p>Placing <code>@Transient</code> on getter with private field worked for me.</p>\n<pre><code>    private String name;\n\n    @Transient\n    public String getName() {\n        return name;\n    }\n\n    public void setName(String name) {\n        this.name = name;\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
